@startuml
title State machine for Staff Member

state Unassigned
state Assigned
state Switched
state Unemployed
state Archived

[*] --> Unassigned : /assignStaffMember

Unassigned --> Assigned : assignedToClient\nor\nassignedToCampaign

Assigned --> Switched : switchedAssignment\n[during work period]

Switched --> Assigned : switchedBack\n[to previous assignment]

Assigned --> Unemployed : staffMemberLeftJob\n[mark as unemployed]

Unemployed --> Archived : archiveRecord\n[after some time has passed]

Archived --> [*] : /unarchiveRecord

@enduml
